Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:35.94,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay Club
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:32.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Prison role playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:35.94,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I play the prisoner, and he plays the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give me some more detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:40.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Like some examples of what you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:41.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't mean in a dirty way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:44.42,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even relevant?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.69,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,He would always handcuff and blindfold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:50.50,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,our girls before running off without paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:52.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Can you be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:55.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How about we reenact the scene with me playing the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:57.13,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, do you still remember why we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:00.88,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that he's a dangerous guy with backdoor gang connections,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.80,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so our hands are tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:05.75,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm also a backdoor kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:08.18,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So could you head out the backdoor and wait in those handcuffs for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.65,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:13.65,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,So we just have to get him to pay up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.14,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:16.53,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.96,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:21.35,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,I would like the prison role playing service again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:26.75,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, I am impressed to see you wearing a guard uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:30.67,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Weekly Ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:30.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,However, I am sorry to say that tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:34.17,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You will be the prisoner, and I will be the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:37.62,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Remove that filthy hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:39.68,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You want some time in the disciplinary room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.93,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to play prison guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.49,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,you need to pay what you owe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Or else you're headed straight to the slammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:51.01,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You prisoners are only walking free because I allow you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:55.18,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,That hand better be removed when I stop smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think they'll be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.94,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,sending you somewhere else instead of the slammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.78,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.98,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Remove the hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.63,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have another chance to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:06.45,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,correct your mistake once I throw your ass in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:09.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Throw my ass in jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:14.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see you try it, you sick warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:20.72,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,So in the Second Season of Prison Break, They've Already Broken Out of Prison, But the Name Works Once You Realize That Society is a Prison
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:23.10,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,I have a depraved samurai here who
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:24.89,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,was making threats and took a couple of kids
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.64,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,to an adult establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.22,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.73,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Warden Beri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:36.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody told me this would happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:39.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay for that thug to be a prison guard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out! I'm innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The real culprit is that sick warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:44.99,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:48.99,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Save your yapping for roll call, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to be part of any roll call.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.25,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,That nasty fellow threw you in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.01,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You won't last long if you disobey him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.71,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzunosuke Beri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.71,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,He's the head warden here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:08.48,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,He's involved in a lot of dirty business such as torturing prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.71,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,The law won't do you any good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.52,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,We're in his kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:17.54,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long before my people produce evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:20.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,that I was framed and prove my innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.28,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:26.48,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,After a lot of running around,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.00,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,we were able to get your sentence reduced!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:31.29,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Only two years of prison time! You'll be out in no time! Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Only two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:35.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,...my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting like this is good news when it's terrible news?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.11,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, there's already been
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.49,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,a lot of information manipulation going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:47.31,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,The report has Gin-chan as the one who was making trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.51,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,and it even says that you assaulted that guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So he's blaming me for the crime and his freaky role playing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:58.65,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That warden was always a troublemaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.98,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,but his father happens to be a big cop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.98,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,with enough connections to get him this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.32,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,His ass is covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.60,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we'll have to poke around some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:13.72,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll do what we can, so hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.33,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your asshole safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If our positions were switched
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.30,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and they'd been thrown in prison for robbing a bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.75,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'd sneak into the prison with an escape plan tattooed all over me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,if that's what it takes to save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:34.35,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Youngster, sometimes there is perspective to be gained by giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:37.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Were you also framed by that rotten guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.27,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just your average two-bit criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.66,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.29,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember that far back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.86,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.48,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that I still have...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.84,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,...210 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Guard! Please put me in a different room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:58.66,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I used to plot ways to escape, but I gave up a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:05:59.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:02.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And what'd you do to warrant a 200-year sentence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:03.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's like Demon King Piccolo level!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:08.38,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, I've realized what I should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:12.35,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing? It's a lovely day outside. We had rice, fish, miso soup, and takuan for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:11.18,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You were writing a letter earlier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:11.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.45,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't given up on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.80,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Put yourself in the shoes of a son
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:20.44,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,who receives letters from his criminal of a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:26.03,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Good warden, I appreciate your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.45,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.70,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you're on the inside or the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.76,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing comes free in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:36.00,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I paid you at the beginning of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.90,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You're only allowed to receive stuff from the outside once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:44.00,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I'm putting in the effort to bring you letters every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.06,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You enjoy shaking old geezers for change?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need the money to play a crane game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.64,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it, Newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.26,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Crane game...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:56.85,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds about right,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:07:00.56,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,since I love playing with the toys in this pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.86,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know how to have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let me join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.08,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,This is my personal privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:08.68,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play with you soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I already had my fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, is this what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you owe me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.33,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.00,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, you looked like one of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:25.21,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,those ugly stuffed animals in a crane game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.71,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.47,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:37.97,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You'll soon find out what happens to people who oppose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.09,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.49,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I told you to behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.56,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you're trying to show your appreciation, give me your dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:53.78,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting my pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:54.98,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll give you my sliced radishes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.77,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,tomorrow and the day after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:59.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're just giving me the stuff you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.22,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What was in the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:04.68,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Just some small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:09.66,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're bribing that warden so you can make small talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:12.78,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other use for my money when I'm stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.26,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,here another 200 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:19.26,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an old man in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.84,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that my family has suffered because of my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:29.02,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,But my son's the only one left to make amends with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:34.28,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected him to reply or forgive me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:38.99,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,but soon, I was receiving replies regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:46.29,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm basically living for the sake of his small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just have him visit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.21,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of going through all this trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.28,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,A felon like me isn't allowed visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:56.30,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,But after spending years writing letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.44,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a model prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:01.68,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,In one week, they'll grant me clemency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.06,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to see your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.23,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, in one week,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.82,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,as long as there isn't any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.32,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you've been thrown in here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.32,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,for a crime you didn't commit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:19.19,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,But for one week, until I meet my son,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.00,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I ask that you don't make any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.58,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.42,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:26.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to help sustain your lifestyle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so you should help me with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.88,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:39.10,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.26,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a model prisoner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you making a huge fuss over pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:47.99,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.65,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Give back my bouncy pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you care more about your son or your pudding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.44,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,My s-sonding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is a sonding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The title of some Jump Square series?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.53,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's all the noise about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Just having a discussion about a bouncy pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.43,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.91,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's an erect pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a bouncy pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.26,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,'Fess up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:06.82,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly an erect pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:08.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's most definitely a bouncy pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You were about to lose your chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.80,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to see your son because of a pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:16.84,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.80,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You better give me my pudding back once the week is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.68,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:26.68,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that you don't want any trouble with the warden...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I understand perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:32.69,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,These guys want to make trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:35.05,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.95,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Shachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:43.37,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,A vicious felon who was locked up on the Devil's Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:47.45,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,but the warden used his connections to bring him here as an underling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.10,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,The King of Criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.46,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Shachi the Killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:53.02,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:58.09,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, so you're the newbie with a lot of spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.59,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,The warden told us about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:05.36,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,He said there were a couple of punching bags that wouldn't fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:08.59,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Some new toys for us to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.56,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Shachi, which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.23,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I would prefer the younger one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.90,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,but I like the idea of beating an old man to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.45,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:25.20,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:30.00,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care if you never get to see your son again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.00,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,No! He's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There are jellyfish on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:44.18,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.53,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Those are for fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.60,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,To show that he's the king of this prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And your gloves are so worn that your fingers are sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:52.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You should patch them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,since I'm the only one who seems to have noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.37,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You making fun of him, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.68,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't jellyfish! They're shoulder pads!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.57,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's how they're supposed to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What? You all knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:05.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been holding back your laughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.81,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:09.33,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is Shachi's new snappy outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:14.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So you cut the fingers off your gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:19.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You could just take off the gloves if they're too tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Are the scars on your forehead the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You cut yourself up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:25.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it wouldn't make sense for actual scars to be so perfectly aligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:26.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you hurt yourself like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.03,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.54,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Just drop the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.19,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Don't provoke Shachi anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:36.23,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:38.56,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,My face was all itchy from a mosquito bite,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.30,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,and when I scratched it, my forehead ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.52,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Shachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.15,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You're blushing, Shachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.70,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You're destroying your image!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:48.52,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I wanted an X on my forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:51.49,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with turning it into a semicolon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.58,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Shachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.67,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You look cool! The X is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.33,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! You're rocking that X!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.59,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I look cool or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:03.01,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't care how my clothes look if they're comfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:06.09,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never gonna wear shoulder pads again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.57,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,A hissy fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.09,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Shachi's throwing a hissy fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:09.85,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:12.55,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,You said that someone was laughing at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.87,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:15.20,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was laughing at you, Shachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.25,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me who it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.19,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,No, Shachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.08,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,He's messing with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.52,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,You're letting him mess with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:22.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:26.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I might be in prison, but I ain't lousy enough to squeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.03,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.30,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.62,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Is he protecting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:36.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If I squeal, you'll kill him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:41.05,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to cause any trouble right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.76,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.53,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,If I let this go, my street cred is ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:49.18,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That would be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:54.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have to rat out my buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And you won't have to kill yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're both grown men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:02.78,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So man up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.71,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's the second time I've seen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.78,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,a person with that look in this cesspool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.45,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Boys, line up and close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.29,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.66,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.29,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:23.55,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't see anything happen, and we know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:26.04,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see this coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:26.80,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.48,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,What is he trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:29.59,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:31.63,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.51,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to use this chance to run away, newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.60,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.36,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:46.36,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:50.40,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:51.87,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:53.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If I only punished one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.81,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd be able to tell who it was from his injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:59.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll just have everyone share the pain, and you can let this go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of your buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:08.56,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:15.76,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you got in a big fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:18.59,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, we just had a little internal scuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.05,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:21.15,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me my pudding, old timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.28,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:28.15,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, don't think you'll get away with disrespecting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.11,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.44,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:39.96,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.19,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,After the newbie turned Shachi's gang to his side,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.98,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,the warden continued to harass him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.79,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, freaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:52.33,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Katou, the guard here had something stolen from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.76,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be searching each cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:58.02,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,I found a strange DVD in cell 316!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:00.59,Main01,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,That's my porn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.90,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Cell 316...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.16,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Sakata, it was you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.68,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You're headed straight to the disciplinary room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:10.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I steal a DVD when I'm stuck in a cell without a TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.91,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't had any contact with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.87,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,The cover is all you needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't let the cover fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.12,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I also check the images on the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.24,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:23.67,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this DVD was under your bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:28.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Warden, nobody said anything about this DVD being under my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know where it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.09,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your chatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:35.16,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him pull the DVD out from under your bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You saw him pull it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:42.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you notice that the cover had been removed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:45.57,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.43,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed that DVD once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.98,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,And it had a cover back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.10,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,With images on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.16,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:54.14,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,There was a cover on it yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.99,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You must be trying to conceal the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:57.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:00.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If it was there yesterday and it's gone now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:03.86,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,the person who removed the cover must be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:10.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for confessing to the crime, Warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.09,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Bound Prisoner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.09,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.31,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Could he have slipped it in then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.86,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:19.00,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are, trying to frame our bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.38,Main01,Men,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:20.86,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.69,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,A guard stealing?! Have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:24.85,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,You should cut open your belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:28.42,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Seppuku! Seppuku! Seppuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.42,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.86,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,He turned my own trap against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:33.03,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Seppuku! Seppuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Boys, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he just shifted the blame on me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.83,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,because he forgot to return the DVD.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:44.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let him have his cover art,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,since that's all the warden apparently needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:49.71,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,He definitely isn't getting any!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:57.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that guy is a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:00.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not equipped to deal with a kid in puberty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.58,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Did he finish his letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:04.15,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:07.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The evil guard is delivering mail in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:10.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:12.64,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:15.85,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,When an evil guard comes to see you in secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:18.94,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,it's either to make a deal or to make a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.18,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.74,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm offering to set you free?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.30,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,It's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.75,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to start a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:31.25,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Play the role of a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:35.60,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,If you do as I say, I'll give you a ticket to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just cut to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You want to screw up the plans of Gramps here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:45.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,All that pestering him for money was just to provoke him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:49.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You were trying to drive him into making trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were picking a fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted him to be associated with a troublemaker
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so you could get his clemency revoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:58.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So he won't be able to see his son...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you keep delivering his letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.35,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:08.00,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I enjoy playing with the toys in this pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:12.57,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Give that letter to Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.48,Main01,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes time to break a toy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:20.55,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the higher they are, the harder they fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.47,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:31.81,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Say "ahhh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you turning my happy dessert time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.32,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,into a Resident Evil moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:40.94,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Because you don't seem to have much of an appetite...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:43.00,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you've been spreading T-Virus everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to Raccoon City!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.45,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat it for you then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:51.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A living corpse should eat porridge and go, "Itchy. Tasty."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:57.51,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I believe that you sent out that letter for me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:58.70,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:01.14,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a reply yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:04.09,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.72,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.01,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Did your long-awaited meeting fall through?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:08.83,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.10,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:14.50,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you send an entry to the Shounen Jump Treasure contest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.27,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a reply?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.90,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:22.29,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,A prisoner was about to kill himself when a reaper appeared before him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:25.49,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be any more emo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.22,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:33.26,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you chased off the warden,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:37.04,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,he's been too embarrassed to show himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:40.55,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,We can use this chance to take revenge on the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,guards who have abused us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.85,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.63,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pull a prison version of Resident Evil
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:49.31,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and teach that evil warden a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:53.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, all of the prisoners will be blamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:58.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You criminals on death row probably don't care,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm an innocent man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.98,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! We're not on death row!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.50,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were born, you've had crows
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,pecking at your brain until it was passport-sized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:09.55,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.94,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get to see my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:13.97,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lose your shot at the Treasure award!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.04,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lost my shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:17.13,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't even started!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:21.00,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Bah, I'll give up since my Treasure award is on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:25.73,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,But Bro, the prisoners here hate the warden's guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.63,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the felons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:30.76,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,They have nothing to lose, so who knows what they'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.40,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,If they get started, we won't be able to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:34.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:40.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You got plenty of troublemakers here, warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:49.41,On Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,Admit Your Own Mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:45.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, you better keep an eye on them if you want to see your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:49.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with the warden before he gets any funny ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:50.91,Main01,Old,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:57.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But it's going to be my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.96,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:34.89,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode:\NEverybody Loves Pajamas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:31.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:33.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody loves pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:34.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Jammies!
